Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尽千辛万苦\N总算到达白灵山圣地的深处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.54,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师和珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.44,0:00:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到在那里\N存在着一股强烈的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.51,0:00:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去救人  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.71,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.95,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.32,0:00:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.06,0:00:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.07,0:00:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.14,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.29,0:01:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.06,0:01:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.02,0:01:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.09,0:01:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.89,0:02:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢  臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.76,0:02:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.17,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要紧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一直通到里面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.11,0:02:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.48,0:02:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有错的\N奈落一定就躲在这里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道奈落\N就躲在神圣的结界里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都赶到了白灵山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要有重大的事发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第118话 白灵山里面又里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股妖气越来越浓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来白灵山神圣的结界\N里面的确藏着一股妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.82,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个回廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子\N它们好像也不打算躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  千万别发动风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吸它们反而会中毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受制裁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为是我看错了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然真的是\N两个血肉之躯的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆的闯进这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还以为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是\N犬夜叉这小子闯进来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个\N也算得上胆大包天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为可以活着离开这里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是要我们\N别再继续往前走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是表示\N奈落一定就在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  往这走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.96,0:04:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  你还是先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.64,0:04:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首要之务\N是查出奈落的所在位置对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.49,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想袭击我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识我神乐用风的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候还东张西望啊你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.95,0:05:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.52,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要撑下去啊  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那哭啊  法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.77,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人先逃\N说不定可以多活一阵子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法发动风穴对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕\N那些会致命的虫毒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也未免太小看我弥勒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己心爱的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要我赴汤蹈火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼了这条命不要也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  真的发动风穴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫毒…发作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢哦  弥勒法师跟珊瑚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你在这边等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去走走观察一下情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉你不是\N无法进入圣地吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我真会\N被这个圣地给消灭掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你不要乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.30,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不知道\N进了圣地会发生什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那么多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你乖乖在这等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间讨论这些有的没的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿帮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.15,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我在这好好保护着戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.16,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师跟珊瑚\N他们两个人上了白灵山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在都还没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好我自己去看一看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟跟真的妖怪比起来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣地应该\N比较不容易影响到我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.77,0:07:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走就快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.17,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准搭她的肩\N也不准跟她说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之\N要是戈薇出了什么事的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定宰了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会有危险啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算半妖也很难闯入圣地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  千万不要逞强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中还要困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要命的尽管上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管来祭这个风穴好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来世间万物\N全都非常爱惜生命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个可恶的法师\N真的一点事都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照理说应该透过风穴\N吸进了大量最猛胜的剧毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师那小子\N简直是自寻死路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一因此送了这条小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有办法再深入追究了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落根本就不在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  不要再过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再发动一次风穴的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里可以弄到衣服穿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.04,0:10:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡路  马上给我滚开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷就是不让
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能怎么样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.52,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件应该可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.84,0:11:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听那班毒虫说\N睡骨已经死了是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡骨兄弟死得好惨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  蛮骨大师兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个\N是睡骨留下来的纪念品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.96,0:11:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇骨  你真的肯给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.36,0:11:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师兄你不是交代过\N一找到就要交出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇骨  你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我的好兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上\N值得我信任的只有你一个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你这个人有点怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就可以消灭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一点事都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.78,0:12:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.49,0:12:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体动不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的没办法\N继续往前走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就走不动啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你也是外强中干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像平常的你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.78,0:13:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没发觉\N一直有人跟着你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你这个家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们七人帮\N人手不太够是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你光剩下一张嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定急着往前走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过继续往前走的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕连你这个半妖\N也会被消灭掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算收拾掉你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别得意得太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.88,0:14:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…还没…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天明明不是朔日啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是结界的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是出乎我意料之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.40,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本以为你会被结界消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只是妖力消失而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.37,0:14:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好处不少嘛  身为一个半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然觉得身体轻松多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  光知道耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是个人类小鬼罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子  看你往哪跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留在这里跟炼骨周旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要想办法\N趁现在闯入山里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挨了一记飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他发动了风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果吸了奈落毒虫的剧毒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.09,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒醒  求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  醒一醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.81,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.45,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你醒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  你先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不走\N我要留下来跟你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.87,0:16:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我这次\N是凶多吉少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  就算只有你\N也一定要好好的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.91,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我丢下你逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿跟你一起死在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.03,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么\N身体渐渐觉得轻松多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些妖怪\N为什么不过来攻击我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们似乎没办法靠近我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这里是圣地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N连我体内的剧毒也被除掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看前面有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  你可以走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子\N是不用一起死在这了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚…说了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全都不记得了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你能够跑多远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.81,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无路可走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.36,0:18:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来  你的死期到了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃进岩石缝里面去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼骨师兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蛇骨你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会跑到这里来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七人帮\N就剩下我们几个了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这件事还真伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我们三个\N凑不足七个人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:19:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要不要再取个新名字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有件事问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡骨身上的\N四魂之玉碎片怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.90,0:20:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把它\N交给蛮骨大师兄啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子还真是没有私心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样一来可就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的四魂之玉碎片\N全都到了蛮骨的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.45,0:20:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定连蛇骨的碎片迟早也…\N叫三人帮好像不够响亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.82,0:20:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会让他得逞\N要叫三杰还是黑暗三人组哩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇骨  其实呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情还真是越来越有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.18,0:20:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山洞怎么这么深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.22,0:20:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道一直通到最里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼骨师兄说的一点都没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.03,0:21:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回人类还是这么可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太开心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.24,0:21:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等很久了\N和你一决胜负的时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.49,0:22:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.26,0:22:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.66,0:22:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.87,0:22:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「喜欢你」 这三个字却始终说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.18,0:22:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.52,0:22:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着镜子 多看一次 看看自己的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.19,0:22:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想飞奔出去追求刺激就得挺起胸膛向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.27,0:23:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆放手去做 直到满意为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.92,0:23:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.69,0:23:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.16,0:23:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.34,0:23:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「喜欢你」 这三个字却始终说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.61,0:23:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.42,0:23:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个木乃伊就是白心上人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.96,0:24:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您生前是\N德高望重的出家人救人无数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在要\N为虎作伥帮助奈落呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们一直当我\N是活菩萨一样供奉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.83,0:24:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我的灵魂\N并未得救赎一直留在黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.47,0:24:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个男人的声音叫醒了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.54,0:24:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是要审判您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.14,0:24:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
